dct_title_s: Carte des Nouvelles Philippines = Kaart der Nieuwe Philippynsche Eylanden
dct_description_sm: Shows the smaller Philippine islands off the coast of Mindanao and the Moluccas. Numbers engraved between the islands represent the number of days it would take for natives to sail between them. J.V.S. = Jacobus van der Schley.
